reviewText: The Doozers are fun to watch as they are always inventing things. Love how they are so colorful as well.
Another good disc to nickle and dime me to death. Would be nice if it didn't have a few of the same episodes, but I really don't care. Keeps the little ones zombified for quite awhile!!!

Fraggle Rock was my favorite show as a kidgrowing up, needless to say i was beyond excited to watch this with my son! He's 4 and really enjoyed this one! Spike, molly bolt, daisy wheel and flex took us on aome very cool adventures. I would recommend this dvd to everyone!
